Messages.Value: Thank you for calling Travel Experts, how may I assist you today? My name is Zoe.
Hi, my name is Emily Smith and I'm calling because I'm having some trouble with my flight.
I'm sorry to hear that, Emily. What seems to be the problem with your flight?
My flight was delayed and I am having trouble making a decision about what to do.
I understand that can be frustrating. Can you tell me a bit more about your travel plans?
Sure. I am traveling from Atlanta, GA to New York City, NY for a business meeting.
I see. Can you tell me what airline you are flying with and the flight number?
I am flying with Delta Airlines and the flight number is DL1234.
And when is your flight scheduled to depart?
My flight is scheduled to depart at 10:00am tomorrow.

I see. According to my system, your flight has been delayed and will now depart at 12:00pm tomorrow. Delta Airlines has offered to book you on a different airline that departs at 10:00am if you would like to switch to that flight. Would you like me to look into that option for you?
Yes, please. That sounds like a good option.
Okay, let me pull up some options for you. One moment please.
I have found a flight with American Airlines that departs at 10:00am tomorrow and arrives in New York City at 12:00pm. Would you like me to make the change for you?
Yes, that sounds like a great option. Thank you for your help!
You're welcome, Emily. I'm glad I could help. Is there anything else I can help you with?
No, that's it. Thank you again.
Of course. Have a great trip!
